*g-cpan-0.16.1 (15 Feb 2010)

  15 Feb 2010; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org> +g-cpan-0.16.1.ebuild:
  Bug #269173: fix hangs on build scripts that expect interactivity. Bug
  #176627: new variable GCPAN_OVERLAY to explicitly select output location
  of new ebuilds. Also GCPAN_CAT for category of new ebuilds. Confirm bug
  #178089 fixed in previous 0.16.0 release. 

